ded the Blu-ray you want to copy into the interface, you&#39;ll see all the disc&#39;s tracks on the left-hand side of the interface. To the right you&#39;re provided with a preview window of movie with the Copy button loaded right above it. You should have no problems copying or archiving your Blu-ray library with this software.","Other Blu-ray copying features include the ability to bypass anti-piracy encryptions. This tool is critical because without it, you could not copy or back up the vast majority of commercial movies.","Additionally, this software allows you to extract and save a Blu-ray&#39;s disc image (ISO file) onto your computer&#39;s hard drive. An ISO file acts as a virtual Blu-ray on your computer. With it, you can watch, archive or make a new physical disc copy – even if you no longer have the original source disc.","In our tests, we found that this Blu-ray copy software application took about 42 minutes to burn a new copy of a Blu-ray from an extracted disc image. This was among the faster times on our lineup."]},"id":"7c403f69-f883-42cc-9c54-41821e71af05","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Output"},"id":"b42732e3-df85-4eda-a190-b94f896beb8a","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/Bs2mhNTLgcUK3pZ3ccrQ54.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/67848-clonebd7.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Bs2mhNTLgcUK3pZ3ccrQ54.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"Bs2mhNTLgcUK3pZ3ccrQ54","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/Bs2mhNTLgcUK3pZ3ccrQ54.jpg","alt":""},"id":"c1d8cc29-44c8-497b-9e0b-f27709d4de00","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["When evaluating Blu-ray copy software, an application&#39;s ability to produce an identical copy of a Blu-ray disc is critical. If the copy is flawed or nonfunctional, it&#39;s a waste of your time and money since you&#39;ll have to burn through multiple blank Blu-rays until you get a good-quality copy. As part of our testing, we asked video experts to inspect the quality of the newly copied test Blu-ray disc. Our experts were unable to detect any difference between the source disc and the copy. If you choose CloneBD Blu-ray Copy, you can trust it to do the job right the first time.","As good as this software is, it leaves out some of the essential tools we look for in the best Blu-ray copy software. Chief among them is that this application cannot compress a full-sized Blu-ray disc onto a smaller-capacity blank. Blank Blu-rays are expensive, and the expensive ones even more so. The product that ranked at the top of our review, <a href=\"/blue-cloner-review\">Blue-Cloner 6</a>, gives you this ability."]},"id":"20f4da0f-6be3-4b20-8f27-c4e0776f37e4","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Customization"},"id":"f650f656-c0fb-4b41-ad98-fd2f94754a46","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/nJePdMLVRKmeUqHLpF7hCP.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/67848-clonebd3.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nJePdMLVRKmeUqHLpF7hCP.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"nJePdMLVRKmeUqHLpF7hCP","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/nJePdMLVRKmeUqHLpF7hCP.jpg","alt":""},"id":"694a9802-98dc-4821-be5b-499feb7bd9f3","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Clone BD Blu-ray Copy&#39;s customization options are a mixed bag. The program gives you three options for copying discs: &#34;Full Movie,&#34; &#34;Main Movie&#34; and &#34;Custom Mode.&#34; Full movie makes an identical copy, Main Movie strips away everything except the feature presentation, and Custom Mode lets you pick and choose which tracks you want on the new disc.","However, the Custom Mode button is greyed-out, which means it&#39;s a nonfunctional option for Blu-ray discs. If you&#39;re copying a DVD, though, this tool is available. We found this to be quite odd and hope that future versions allow you make truly customized Blu-ray discs."]},"id":"2c